snippet.title: Official Duke Nukem Forever Teaser Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
New 2011 trailer: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WnrbFOMvKSM

UPDATE: Duke Nukem Forever is set to be released in 2011! Links: http://pax.gamespot.com/story/6275153/duke-nukem-forever-shipping-in-2011-on-360-ps3-pc/
http://kotaku.com/5629782/

for more info and some screenshots go to http://www.3drealms.com/duke4/
